724430f-b.title: Manhattan: West End Avenue - 61st Street (West)
724430f-b.text:
West End Ave., east side, north from and including West 6lst Street,
and showing an automobile junk yard occupying the 6lst to 62nd Street
block front. View No. 2 emphasises the latter.
November 25, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
